These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: animation, spy, western, thriller, drama, zombie, time-travel
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
4. the person watching drama movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching western movies##2
5. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching animation movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | western | drama | animation | thriller | spy | zombie |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: pumpkin, apple, mango, peach, cranberry, potato, cucumber
1. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
3. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
4. the person eating mango is between the person eating peach and the person eating pumpkin##2
5. the person eating peach is on the left of the person eating apple##1
6. the person eating mango is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Food   | potato | cucumber | pumpkin | mango | peach | apple | cranberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, bongani, bluemaster, dannemann, havana, aristoff, bolivar
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
5. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
6. the havana-smoker is between the aristoff-smoker and the bongani-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Cigar   | bolivar | aristoff | havana | bongani | davidoff | bluemaster | dannemann |

