.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta, tea, almond-milk, soy-milk, 7up, mirinda
1. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking soy-milk##2
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
7. the person drinking tea is the person drinking tea##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |      4      |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Beverage   | 7up | fanta | almond-milk | mirinda | soy-milk | sprite | tea |

