.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-5::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, ship, airplane, taxi, tram, van, roller
1. the person driving the van is between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the tram##2
2. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the taxi is the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
6. the person driving the airplane is between the person driving the tram and the person driving the ship##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |      4       |   5   |     6     |   7    |
| Transport   | roller | taxi | van | tram | airplane | ship | scooter |

